attributes.title: ABAOLUTELY TERRIBLE 😡😤🧚🏻✨
attributes.review: This app not only took 1 YEAR to download... but also hacked my phone and i could no longer use it without a big notification popping up on the screen stating “VOTE TRUMP 2020” Last week i heard a knock on the door and turns out IT WAS TRUMP HIMSELF. his body guards tied me up to a chair and gagged me with a sock and told me i could go nowhere unless i promised to vote for him and tell all my friends and family. now this was a BAD thing for me being a poc. i promised to do so and told all my friends and family. he continued to call me me asking if i told them and i told him i did but they laughed and me and will not be voting for him. after i told him this i immediately regretted it bc he sent a private jet to my house that took me away to a tiny room that was like a jail cell. he continued to keep me there for months witg no food or water. i had to poop and pee on the floor. when all the protests happened he decided to let me go as long as i went to them as a trump supporter. i agreed and once i got home got all my stuff and fled the country. i am now hiding out in europe where i will be staying witg some cute french people.

attributes.title: Taylor Swift is haunting me
attributes.review: This app did not download until I put in my SSN, it took a week and a half to download, and every time I open it, it crashes my phone, deletes all my pictures, and texts my ex “I miss you”. Who designed this???? It will set off notifications every hour, and the sound is the entire Taylor Swift 1989 album and it won’t stop playing no matter what I do until it’s finished. It also calls me and my mother a b*tch and tried selling my sister to Elon Musk. After I download it, I came home and my house was robbed, and my entire basement was missing. My lawn was painted orange, and all my garden gnomes were turned inside out. :( easily worst app in the store
